This is Phish: I-90s, a DryGoods bonus CD compilation featuring archival material from as early as nineteen years before the Live In Utica DVD/CD release (compiled by Phish Archivist Kevin Shapiro). This collection of highlights follows the band along the I-90 New York Thruway as they honed their skills in drummer Jon Fishman's home state, recalling highlights from some of the region's many great Phish shows in the 90s.
